snippet.title: Blade & Sorcery: Nomad l Oculus Quest 2
snippet.description: Blade & Sorcery: Nomad is a built-for-VR medieval fantasy sandbox with full physics driven melee, ranged and magic combat. Become a powerful warrior, ranger or sorcerer and devastate your enemies.
